description: Another busy day in the office. I guess, there are so many boys looking for the job in Prague. The first one looked like a musician from Ireland but in reality he was a car mechanic. A bit shy young man got very lively in the end. Looks can be deceptive sometimes. The second boy was a bit nervous about my secretary. I think, he liked her a lot. He asked for 45 000. I laughed out loud at that outrageous demand, I couldn´t help it. Dream on! I couldn´t wait to put him in his place. To his defence, he was quite cute. So I couldn´t be too hard on him. The last guy today was very sweet. A well-built hockey player, intelligent and good looking. I could tell he was ambitious and loving money. How did these three lads responded to my dirty offer?
title: Dirty Scout 16
